# Full integration test — exercises all 4 learned operation types in one run.
#
# The compiler growth loop will:
#   1. Look up (or learn) an ADD rule via the LLM + real Vortex simx
#   2. Look up (or learn) a MUL rule via the LLM + real Vortex simx
#   3. Look up (or learn) a LOAD rule via the LLM + real Vortex simx
#   4. Look up (or learn) a LOOP rule via the LLM + real Vortex simx
#      (The loop verifies multi-instruction control-flow with BNE + ADDI)
#
# Each operation is independently compiled, run on real hardware (simx),
# verified for correctness, and cycle-counted before its rule is committed.

r3 = add(r1, r2)
r4 = mul(r1, r2)
r5 = load(r6)
r1 = loop(r1)
